OL,3,CDozens of MPs still working as
OL,4,Ccouncillors, despite calls to step down
OL,6,FBy ITV News Political Correspondent
OL,7,FHarry Horton and Senior Politics
OL,8,FProducer Maya Bowles
OL,10,FDozens of MPs have stayed in their
OL,11,Froles as councillors since the general
OL,12,Felection, despite calls for many to
OL,13,Fresign from their local government
OL,14,Froles.
OL,16,FThere are currently 26 MPs who also
OL,17,Fserve on local councils, including 12
OL,18,FLiberal Democrats, nine Labour MPs,
OL,19,Ffour Conservatives and one Independent.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/19
