OL,3,CDozens of MPs still working as
OL,4,Ccouncillors, despite calls to step down
OL,6,FITV News revealed earlier this year
OL,7,Fthat almost 10% of all MPs were still
OL,8,Fworking as councillors after July's
OL,9,Fgeneral election, but since our report
OL,10,Faround 36 have resigned from their
OL,11,Flocal government posts.
OL,13,FThe 26 MPs still balancing the two
OL,14,Fjobs insist they're able to do both,
OL,15,Fdespite many facing fierce local
OL,16,Fopposition and calls to step down.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/19
