OL,6,FAnalysis of local council attendance
OL,7,Fdata also shows that the majority of
OL,8,Fthe MPs still doing both jobs are
OL,9,Fshowing up to less than 50% of council
OL,10,Fmeetings since getting elected to
OL,11,FParliament.
OL,13,FITV News analysis found that 14 of the
OL,14,F26 MPs have an attendance rate of 50%
OL,15,For less, with some going to as few as
OL,16,F13% of meetings.
