OL,4,Ccouncillors, despite calls to step down
OL,6,FLabour says all of their nine MPs also
OL,7,Fworking as councillors had agreed a
OL,8,Fdate to stand down "dependent on local
OL,9,Fcircumstances". However, at least one
OL,10,FLabour MP has told ITV News that no
OL,11,Fsuch date has been agreed.
OL,13,FNone of the 26 MPs serve on councils
OL,14,Fholding local elections this May. They
OL,15,Fargue that standing down would trigger
OL,16,Fby-elections, which could be costly
OL,17,Ffor the taxpayer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/19
